description:
Follow Cercle behind the scenes of Cercle Odyssey, the new 360° immersive concert experience.

ABOUT CERCLE ODYSSEY

We’re almost ready to unveil Cercle Odyssey, a series of unique and immersive solo shows spanning across 15 breathtaking dates—from Mexico City to Paris, with a stop in Los Angeles. This time, we’re bringing nature and the Cercle experience even closer to you.

After more than a year on this insane journey, working on a project that goes beyond anything we’ve done until now, we’re proud to share the first episode of our Behind the Scenes series. This journey has already been extraordinary: filled with wild ideas, unexpected challenges, doubts, joys and moments of pure awe. All of this carried by a team so dedicated, driven by the same passion for music, the same love for the world’s beauty around us, the same desire to give to people one-of-a-lifetime experiences.
In this episode, we invite you backstage to witness this project coming true. This series is for you, who
